---
import LayoutFunnel from '@/layouts/LayoutFunnel.astro';
---

<LayoutFunnel title="Fitness Revenue Architecture | Marketing by Bešić">
  <!-- Hero Section -->
  <section class="min-h-screen flex items-center justify-center py-20">
    <div class="container-custom max-w-4xl text-center">
      <div class="w-20 h-20 bg-brand/10 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-8">
        <svg class="w-10 h-10 text-brand" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
          <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M3 6l3 1m0 0l-3 1a5.002 5.002 0 006.828 4.828A5 5 0 0012 12a5 5 0 005.172-4.172A5.002 5.002 0 0021 12l-3-1m0 0l3-1m-3 1l3 1M3 6v12m18-12v12M9 9h6m-6 4h6m-6 4h6" />
        </svg>
      </div>

      <h1 class="heading-xl mb-6">
        Scale Your Fitness Business With Predictable Revenue
      </h1>
      <p class="body-lg mb-12">
        Neurolinguistic Revenue Architecture for fitness studios, gyms, and personal training businesses. Stop chasing leads. Start converting members.
      </p>

      <!-- Hero Image Placeholder -->
      <div class="w-full h-[500px] bg-[#1a1a1a] border border-[#8224e3]/30 flex items-center justify-center rounded-lg text-gray-500 mb-12">[HERO IMAGE PLACEHOLDER: 1200x600]</div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Problem Section -->
  <section class="py-20">
    <div class="container-custom max-w-3xl">
      <h2 class="heading-lg mb-8 text-center">Why Your Fitness Business Is Leaving Money on the Table</h2>
      <p class="body-md mb-6">
        Fitness businesses lose an average of 35% of potential revenue through poor lead follow-up, weak retention systems, and messaging that doesn't resonate with your ideal member. You're working harder, not smarter.
      </p>
      <p class="body-md">
        Our Diagnostic Protocol maps your entire member journey and identifies the exact points where revenue is leaking out of your business.
      </p>

      <!-- Image Placeholder -->
      <div class="w-full h-[300px] bg-[#1a1a1a] border border-[#8224e3]/30 flex items-center justify-center rounded-lg text-gray-500 my-12">[IMAGE PLACEHOLDER: 800x400]</div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Solution Section -->
  <section class="py-20">
    <div class="container-custom max-w-3xl">
      <h2 class="heading-lg mb-8 text-center">The NRA Fitness Framework</h2>

      <!-- Phase 1 -->
      <div class="bg-bg-secondary border border-white/5 rounded-xl p-8 mb-6 text-left">
        <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
          <div class="w-10 h-10 bg-brand/10 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0">
            <span class="text-brand font-bold">1</span>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="font-heading text-xl font-bold mb-2">Phase 1: 30-Day Diagnostic Audit</h3>
            <p class="body-md">
              Zero ad spend. We analyze your current lead flow, membership retention, and communication systems. You'll receive a comprehensive diagnostic report showing exactly where revenue is leaking.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Phase 2 -->
      <div class="bg-bg-secondary border border-white/5 rounded-xl p-8 mb-6 text-left">
        <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
          <div class="w-10 h-10 bg-brand/10 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0">
            <span class="text-brand font-bold">2</span>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="font-heading text-xl font-bold mb-2">Phase 2: Conversion Infrastructure</h3>
            <p class="body-md">
              We deploy NLP-optimized messaging, build automated follow-up sequences, and create a member acquisition engine that runs on autopilot. Every lead is nurtured to conversion.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Phase 3 -->
      <div class="bg-bg-secondary border border-white/5 rounded-xl p-8 text-left">
        <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
          <div class="w-10 h-10 bg-brand/10 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0">
            <span class="text-brand font-bold">3</span>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="font-heading text-xl font-bold mb-2">Phase 3: Performance Compensation</h3>
            <p class="body-md">
              You only pay on verified net-new memberships. No vanity metrics. No wasted ad spend. Pure, measurable growth tied directly to your membership numbers.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Image Placeholder -->
      <div class="w-full h-[300px] bg-[#1a1a1a] border border-[#8224e3]/30 flex items-center justify-center rounded-lg text-gray-500 my-12">[IMAGE PLACEHOLDER: 800x400]</div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Execution Gap Section -->
  <section class="py-20 bg-[#111111] relative z-10">
    <div class="container-custom max-w-3xl">
      <h2 class="heading-lg mb-8 text-center">The Execution Gap</h2>
      <p class="body-md mb-6 text-center">
        Most agencies deliver reports. We deliver revenue. The gap between knowing your leaks and fixing them is where businesses die. Our framework closes that gap by implementing, tracking, and optimizing every touchpoint in your member journey.
      </p>
      <p class="body-md text-center">
        While your competitors are still waiting for proposals, your fitness business will already be capturing the revenue they're leaving on the table.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA / Calendar Section -->
  <section class="py-20 pb-48">
    <div class="container-custom max-w-3xl text-center">
      <h2 class="heading-lg mb-6">Schedule Your Diagnostic Audit</h2>
      <p class="body-lg mb-12">
        Book a free 15-minute call to see if your fitness business qualifies for the NRA framework.
      </p>

      <!-- Booking Button -->
      <div class="mt-12 flex justify-center w-full">
        <a
          href="https://calendar.app.google/EnAH7N1F2bYFdUa9A"
          target="_blank"
          rel="noopener noreferrer"
          class="inline-flex items-center justify-center px-8 py-4 text-lg font-bold text-white transition-all duration-300 bg-[#8224e3] rounded-lg hover:bg-[#6a1ca6] hover:scale-105 shadow-[0_0_20px_rgba(130,36,227,0.4)]"
        >
          Book Your Diagnostic Call
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</LayoutFunnel>
